Listening to high-volume music for a long time using portable music devices such as Mp3 players can cause permanent hearing damage.
As far as the European Commission is concerned, in a communiqué circulated in Brussels, it cites the opinion of the EU’s newly identified and emerging (Csrseri) Scientific Commission on health risks, published today.
